race.comment: BLUE LACE (1) is a progressive dog who scored her 2nd career win last time at this track, scoring by a neck (17.68). Looks a key chance if runs up to latest figure. SOUTH CRENSHAW (2) has shown good improvement at his last two starts, most recently finishing 2nd at this track over 300m. Although beaten ran one of the quickest times on the card last start. Expecting another good run. SALUTING CRAIG (3) scored well last start as odds-on favourite by half a length at this track in a handy 17.66 beating Son Of Zatara. Draws to advantage and in form and has the ability. Significant danger.
